1072
01:35:00,340 --> 01:35:02,740
Yes. Yeah, of course he would.

1073
01:35:03,110 --> 01:35:05,840
To tell a story so well it becomes real.

1074
01:35:06,413 --> 01:35:09,109
The perfect con. That's his whole...

1075
01:35:10,818 --> 01:35:12,342
God damn it, that's what.

1076
01:35:12,419 --> 01:35:14,182
You know what? We don't know.

1077
01:35:15,489 --> 01:35:17,548
- We better transfer the money.
- Son of a...

1078
01:35:17,624 --> 01:35:19,615
It's your brother's life.

1079
01:35:21,128 --> 01:35:23,119
I'm gonna wire the money.

1080
01:35:30,904 --> 01:35:32,030
Okay.

1081
01:35:39,546 --> 01:35:41,878
I'm coming in with you.

1082
01:35:42,316 --> 01:35:43,806
No, stay here.

1083
01:35:45,586 --> 01:35:48,646
Going in alone is a very
important thing to do.

1084
01:35:53,427 --> 01:35:55,019
I'm so scared.

1085
01:35:58,599 --> 01:36:02,091
Anything I can imagine
finding in there, I'm scared of.

1086
01:36:04,104 --> 01:36:06,572
I'm gonna be here when you come out.

1087
01:36:43,710 --> 01:36:45,075
Stephen?

1088
01:36:51,785 --> 01:36:53,275
Stephen?

1089
01:36:57,090 --> 01:36:59,456
Game's up. Come on out.

1090
01:37:03,263 --> 01:37:05,925
Come on, let's blow this one-hat town.

1091
01:37:41,835 --> 01:37:43,769
- Stephen!
- No, Bloom.

1092
01:37:48,542 --> 01:37:50,134
Did Penelope wire the money?

1093
01:37:50,644 --> 01:37:51,838
Yeah.

1094
01:37:56,750 --> 01:37:59,014
Stephen, tell me what this is.

1095
01:37:59,086 --> 01:38:01,418
Jesus Christ, Bloom, I'm sorry.

1096
01:38:01,488 --> 01:38:04,150
I don't need sorry. I need the truth.

1097
01:38:06,660 --> 01:38:09,185
God damn it, Stephen.
You tell me what to do.

1098
01:38:09,262 --> 01:38:10,991
- Get the hell out of here now!
- Tell me the truth.

1099
01:38:11,064 --> 01:38:13,328
Is this a con or is it real?

1100
01:38:15,268 --> 01:38:16,860
A con?

1101
01:38:18,972 --> 01:38:20,599
It's real, Bloom.

1102
01:38:24,478 --> 01:38:26,139
<i>Hello, Bloom.</i>

1103
01:38:26,213 --> 01:38:28,181
God damn it, Bloom.
It's real, this is not a con.

1104
01:38:28,248 --> 01:38:31,581
<i>Are you happy to hear</i>
<i>from your old Diamond Dog?</i>

1105
01:38:31,651 --> 01:38:35,280
These are the Dog's men.
He's crossed us for revenge.

1106
01:38:35,589 --> 01:38:36,988
Damn it, Bloom, run!

1107
01:38:37,057 --> 01:38:39,787
<i>I told you Stephen would fall.</i>

1108
01:38:40,994 --> 01:38:44,054
<i>And you? You are paralyzed,</i>

1109
01:38:44,698 --> 01:38:48,691
<i>praying this is just</i>
<i>another one of Stephen's stories.</i>

1110
01:38:49,236 --> 01:38:50,703
<i>Is it?</i>

1111
01:38:51,338 --> 01:38:54,398
<i>Close your eyes now, sweet child.</i>

1112
01:38:55,442 --> 01:38:58,639
<i>And I will tell you the truth.</i>

1113
01:39:02,315 --> 01:39:03,373
No!

1114
01:39:15,462 --> 01:39:16,724
Bloom!

1115
01:39:23,236 --> 01:39:24,999
He's got another gun!

1116
