1121
01:40:31,438 --> 01:40:33,497
Can I get a "wow" for this?

1122
01:40:36,143 --> 01:40:37,269
Wow.

1123
01:40:39,779 --> 01:40:42,247
You son of a bitch.

1124
01:40:52,959 --> 01:40:55,052
