01:41:08,008 --> 01:41:09,771
Tastes like tinfoil.

1127
01:41:10,644 --> 01:41:14,205
All right, here's what I want you to do.
Bang Bang split?

1128
01:41:14,581 --> 01:41:16,071
Yeah. Clean exit.

1129
01:41:16,149 --> 01:41:17,173
How?

1130
01:41:17,350 --> 01:41:18,681
Car bomb.

1131
01:41:18,752 --> 01:41:19,844
Good.

1132
01:41:20,120 --> 01:41:22,111
- Penelope?
- She's outside.

1133
01:41:22,189 --> 01:41:23,781
All right, here's what.

1134
01:41:24,858 --> 01:41:27,986
<i>Take Penelope to Helsinki,</i>
<i>get that flight to Rio.</i>

1135
01:41:28,061 --> 01:41:30,552
<i>Play out the whole</i>
<i>"on the run from vengeful Russians" thing,</i>

1136
01:41:30,630 --> 01:41:33,155
<i>that'll be fun for her.</i>
<i>Play it like I'm dead, actually.</i>

1137
01:41:33,233 --> 01:41:35,326
That'll add some gravity to everything.

1138
01:41:35,402 --> 01:41:37,529
And I'll see you when I see you.

1139
01:41:38,572 --> 01:41:41,268
- When?
- I don't know. Not too soon, I hope.

1140
01:41:41,341 --> 01:41:44,003
Last thing you need is me hanging around.

1141
01:41:44,077 --> 01:41:46,739
Anyway, how am I going to top this?

1142
01:41:47,113 --> 01:41:48,375
Bloom,

1143
01:41:49,783 --> 01:41:51,216
pick a card.

1144
01:41:53,320 --> 01:41:55,379
- All right.
- Got it?

1145
01:41:55,889 --> 01:41:57,220
Yeah.

1146
01:42:04,998 --> 01:42:07,899
That's the best card trick I've ever seen.

1147
01:42:09,836 --> 01:42:12,202
Wish you had a bigger audience.

1148
01:42:12,639 --> 01:42:15,369
You're the only audience I ever needed.

1149
01:42:26,753 --> 01:42:28,118
I love you.

1150
01:42:31,157 --> 01:42:32,283
Bye.

1151
01:42:40,634 --> 01:42:41,862
Shh. Shh. Shh.

1152
01:42:41,935 --> 01:42:44,130
It's okay. It's okay.

